Clone repo to server

Update .env with secure passwords

Run sudo ./install.sh

Access services via browser:
| Service       | Port |
| ------------- | ---- |
| Portainer     | 9000 |
| Grafana       | 3000 |
| MinIO Console | 9001 |
| Traefik UI    | 8080 |

This gives you a fully functional, modular NETLIFEGY Cloud v1 that you can later extend to a full SaaS platform with:

User accounts

Project management

Git-based deployments

Multi-tenant isolation
